messageBody:
Dear all

I am coming back to Junit having not touched it for ages and have just
installed it on my new laptop. I have downloaded and unzipped 3.8.1.
The textui runner tests pass OK (119 run) but the swingui tests fail to
run - java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError:junit/textui/ResultPrinter

I have checked and rechecked the CLASSPATH and PATH settings and they
seem okay. Has anybody got any ideas what could be wrong?

Thanks in advance.

Cheers, APC
